{"tid":830222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞狗打劫","createTime":"2018-09-21T04:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T04:35:34.000Z","uid":211090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"23e2468c309fae135d67c91dcb7534bc049d0a97","tid":830222,"uid":211090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:30:13.000Z","msg":"早上10時半左右，紅磡發生搶劫案。兩名男子行經鶴園東街與紅磡道交界時，遭兩名蒙面賊人持刀襲擊，搶去兩個背囊；據報背囊內內有74萬美元。賊人得手後，跳上接應的白色私家車，車上有兩同黨，逃去無蹤；兩名事主一人為本地人，另一人為南亞裔，同告中刀相繼送院。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報趕到，現正追緝4名南亞匪徒，並在全港各主要道路採取「捷進行動」，搜捕賊人及賊車。其中黃大仙龍翔道、西九龍快速公路奧運站外，均可見警員穿著避彈衣和頭盔，荷槍實彈截查可疑車輛，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<blockquote> <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180921/58706789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180921%2F58706789&d=FSuEM9jv38mr8qdJ%2BqezmIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=be1a3d79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180921%2F58706789&h=f020ca1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180921/58706789</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ea145cf3036227c946048f077dc850876b7bdd30","tid":830222,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:31:45.000Z","msg":"香港真係內憂外患，內有蝻，外有蝗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328743f088a615daf0990d0b1e3fddf5a6156668","tid":830222,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:34:13.000Z","msg":"兩名事主一人為本地人，<span style=\"color: red;\">另一人為南亞裔</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c619a400ced969f2e12458c191216b22f5e797a5","tid":830222,"uid":197093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23e2468c309fae135d67c91dcb7534bc049d0a97","tid":830222,"uid":211090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:30:13.000Z","msg":"早上10時半左右，紅磡發生搶劫案。兩名男子行經鶴園東街與紅磡道交界時，遭兩名蒙面賊人持刀襲擊，搶去兩個背囊；據報背囊內內有74萬美元。賊人得手後，跳上接應的白色私家車，車上有兩同黨，逃去無蹤；兩名事主一人為本地人，另一人為南亞裔，同告中刀相繼送院。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報趕到，現正追緝4名南亞匪徒，並在全港各主要道路採取「捷進行動」，搜捕賊人及賊車。其中黃大仙龍翔道、西九龍快速公路奧運站外，均可見警員穿著避彈衣和頭盔，荷槍實彈截查可疑車輛，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<blockquote> <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180921/58706789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180921%2F58706789&d=FSuEM9jv38mr8qdJ%2BqezmIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=be1a3d79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180921%2F58706789&h=f020ca1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180921/58706789</a></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"張超雄萬歲"}]}